Tere Bin Episode 54 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 15th June 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.title: Tiku Weds Sheru - Official Trailer | Nawazuddin Siddiqui, Avneet Kaur | Prime Video India
snippet.description:
Prime Video Presents
Tiku Weds Sheru Official Trailer
Directed by Sai Kabir
Starring Nawazuddin Siddiqui and Avneet Kaur
Produced by Kangana Ranaut

Official Release Date June 23, 2023 on Prime Video 

About:
Sheru and Tiku are marginalized souls from the underprivileged strata of society. They are ambitious for a better life but, life has different plans for them. Shiraz, popularly known as Sheru, hails from Bhopal, a small-town in India. Sheru comes to Mumbai in search of a better life. Being semi-literate, he works as a pimp for a local don, Shahid Bhai, and also as a junior artist as a decoy job, where he finds girls for his pimping business. He risks everything to win the confidence of his boss to be promoted as an equal partner. Taslim, aka Tiku, lives with her large conservative Muslim family in Bhopal. To break free from her family, she runs away to Delhi under the pretext of higher studies, where she falls in love with a man from a different religion, but her family marry her off to the first available eligible bachelor, Sheru. Sheru accepts the proposal in desperation of repaying a loan, while Tiku sees Sheru as her passport to freedom. However, Sheru falls in love with Tiku but they get caught between the chaos of the underworld, drugs, and romance and face one tragedy after the other without any time to deal with their sorrow.

Prime Video is just one of the many benefits of a Prime membership, available for just ₹1499/ year.

Also included are popular global Amazon Originals like Citadel, The Lord of The Rings: The Rings of Power, Reacher, Tom Clancy's Jack Ryan, The Boys, Hunters, Fleabag, The Marvelous Mrs. Maisel, & many more, available for unlimited streaming as part of a Prime membership. Prime Video includes content across Hindi, Marathi, Gujarati, Tamil, Telugu, Kannada, Malayalam, Punjabi, & Bengali. 
Prime Video Mobile Edition: Consumers can also enjoy Prime Video’s exclusive content library with Prime Video Mobile Edition at ₹599 per year. This single-user, mobile-only annual video plan offers everyone access to high-quality entertainment exclusively on their mobile devices. Users can sign-up for this plan via the Prime Video app (on Android) or website. 
Instant Access: Prime Members can watch anywhere, anytime on the Prime Video app for smart TVs, mobile devices, Fire TV, Fire TV stick, Fire tablets, Apple TV, & multiple gaming devices. Prime Video is also available to consumers through Airtel and Vodafone pre-paid & post-paid subscription plans. In the Prime Video app, Prime members can download episodes on their mobile devices & tablets & watch anywhere offline at no additional cost.

Prime Video Channels: Prime Video Channels offers friction-free & convenient access to a wide range of premium content from multiple video streaming services all available at a single destination – Prime Video website & apps. Prime Members can buy add-on subscriptions & enjoy a hassle-free entertainment experience, simplified discovery, frictionless payments, & more. Rent: Consumers can enjoy even more movies from new releases to classic favourites, available to rent – no Prime membership required. View titles available by visiting primevideo.com/store. The rental destination can be accessed via the STORE tab on primevideo.com & the Prime Video app on Android smart phones, smart-TVs, connected STBs, & Fire TV stick.

Episode 3798: Yellow Shagun Ceremony
--------------------------------------------------------
Finally, Pyaarelal's shagun ritual begins. Everyone dresses in yellow attire because Pyaarelal has chosen Sapna as his bride. Dr. Hathi gets excited about the food section, so he starts to taste the food items in advance. Everyone thinks that Popatlal's name change, suggested by Vinu Kaka, was the reason for his marriage. Bagha praises Bawari because the name she suggested proved to be lucky for Pyaarelal. The groom-to-be Pyaarelal, also arrives at the venue wearing a yellow dress and offers his gratitude to Bawari. Sapna's family arrives at Gokuldham, and they get impressed when they see everyone wearing yellow dresses. Stay tuned to learn more!

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 55 Teaser - 15th June 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Director: Siraj ul Haq

snippet.description:

#steffiulagam #steffivlogs #vlogsintamil 

Friends, I hope you will also try gardening and home and grow some fruits and vegetables. All the best and happy gardening.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3799 | 16 June 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3799: Sapna Ki Love Story
--------------------------------------------------------
Everyone has arrived together to perform the shagun ritual of Pyaarelal and Sapna, but Pyaarelal seems to be missing. Someone said that he had visited the nearby temple before the ritual. Pyaarelal returns shortly, but he is accompanied by another young man named Swapnil. Sapna gets flabbergasted when she sees this new fellow. Pyaarelal talks about how he met Swapnil. Swapnil turns out to be Sapna's ex-boyfriend, who left her for a lucrative job offer in Canada. Swapnil's job didn't work out, and now he has returned, but Sapna has moved on. According to Pyaarelal, Swapnil and Sapna still have feelings for each other, so he decides to unite them. Will Pyaarelal sacrifice for Sapna's love story this time?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3799, 16 June 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 53 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Nisa BB Cream - 14th June 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally presented by Nisa BB Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma
Sohail Sameer as Anwar
Sabeena Farooq as Haya
Hira Soomro as Maryam
Fazila Qazi as Aneela
Farhan Ally Agha as Waqas
Seemi Pasha as Sabra
Mahmood Aslam as Malik Mukhtaar
Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa

It is necessary for every road user to be aware of traffic signs and driving rules and regulations. Traffic signs can give you important information that can ensure your safety and the safety of those around you and awareness of road rules can lower chances of accidents.

snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3797: Kalpana Ka Final Decision
--------------------------------------------------------
Kalpana and her parents get upset when they discover that Popatlal has changed his name to Pyaarelal on purpose. Kalpana questions him about the reason behind his name change, to which Pyaarelal answers that, as per Vinu Kaka's sayings, he took this decision. Kalpana isn't convinced by Pyaarelal's reason, and she decides to call off the wedding. Kalpana tells Pyaarelal that he should have at least informed her about the new name. She also tells Pyaarelal that his fickle-minded nature makes it difficult for her to trust him. Pyaarelal, aka Popatlal, gets melancholy that he has to stay a bachelor forever. Watch the episode to learn what happens next!

It was spirit of celebration as we immersed ourselves in joy and colorful event surrounded by family and loved ones. From stunning decorations that will leave you awestruck to the energetic ambiance of the festivities, it will truly blow your mind.
The preparations for this special occasion began the night before, and as the early morning arrived, all of us eagerly got ready for the festivities. Jaanu did makeup for Papa. The presence of our beloved relatives enhanced the joyous atmosphere, and after a few formalities, Ram took charge of lighting up the crackers, infusing the air with the festive spirit.
The burn of summer couldn’t stop us from enjoying, we embarked on a car ride to the grand hall, which Ram had beautifully decorated the night before. Amma's surprise upon seeing the banner was priceless, and the vibrant sounds of drums, dazzling lights, and fragrant flowers elevated the function to new heights.
And of course, what's a celebration without delicious food? The feast was undoubtedly the highlight of the event, tantalizing our taste buds with a delightful spread of culinary delights.
As the evening progressed, we created our own dance floor, embracing the joy of dancing with relatives and honoring cherished traditions. The energy and happiness radiated through every step, forging unforgettable memories.

snippet.title: Washington DC to New York - An American Truck Yatra!
snippet.description:
Continuing on my journey to listen to a variety of voices, I recently went on a 190 km 'American Truck Yatra' from Washington DC to New York. 

Much like my Truck Yatra from Delhi to Chandigarh here in India, I enjoyed a candid heart-to-heart conversation- this time centred around the everyday lives of Indian-origin Truck drivers in America.

Was happy to find out that our brothers in America earn fair wages, and work in a system that is focused on the 'Driver's comfort'. 

The hardworking Truck drivers' community in India deserves a life of dignity too, and an inclusive vision that takes them forward is bound have a positive cascading effect on the economy of our entire country.

#rahulgandhi, #राहुल_गांधी, #bharatjodoyatra, #RahulKiAmericaTruckYatra

A Yatra from Delhi To Chandigarh with Truck Drivers: 
https://youtu.be/LZ9fOkHL6VY


– 

• YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/rahulgandhi
• Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/rahulgandhi
• Twitter: https://twitter.com/rahulgandhi
• Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/rahulgandhi

–

Chapters:-

00:00-00:23 - Introduction 
00:23-03:39 - Washington DC to New York 
03:40-04:42 - Best Features of a US Truck 
04:42-05:13 - How much money do Truck drivers in the US make? 
05:14-06:42 - Message to Indian truck drivers 
06:43-07:16 - BJP rule, Unemployment, and Inflation 
07:16-07:42 - A Tribute to Sidhu Moosewala 
07:43-09.44 - Breakfast at a diner in New York

snippet.title: Udaariyaan | उड़ारियां | Ep. 717 & 718 | Recap
snippet.description:
Udaariyaan | उड़ारियां | Ep. 717 & 718 | Recap

Nehmat makes the difficult decision to raise her child alone by leaving Ekam's house forever. As she moves forward with this choice, Nehmat also feels bad for Harleen upon discovering her infertility. Will she discuss her decision with Harleen?

Hailing from a small village in Punjab, the Sandhu family is driven by one obsession: to leave their sarson ke khet behind & migrate to Canada aka Kaneda! A cruel twist of fate, however, has different plans for the two sisters Tejo & Jasmine when the dashing Fateh comes into their lives. Will the three be able to fulfill their sapon ki Udaariyaan?

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.title: Pagal Ay - @shahatgill  | @buildingpanther  | Kaptaan | Ashu Sidhu | Garry Bhullar | Official Video
snippet.description:
A fresh banger by upcoming pop icon Shahat Gill, ‘Pagal Ay’ featuring Panther is going to make you shake a leg or two! The song is written by the infamous duo Kaptaan with a rap verse by Panther. Composed by Ashu Sidhu, the beats of song are a definite earworm!

#PagalAy #ShahatGill #Panther #NewPunjabiSong #NewDanceSong #DesiHipHop #IndianHipHop #dancesong2023 

Audio Credits:
Singers: Shahat Gill & Panther
Music & Lyrics: Kaptaan
Rap by Panther
Composition: Ashu Sidhu
Produced by NVee & Dhyan Beats

Video Credits:
Video: GarryBhullarFilms 
DOP: Shoeb 
Edit: GOBINDPURIYA 
DI: Garlic Beans Studio 
Costume: Kavya 
Choreographer: Sumit Kumar 
Associate: Bunny Khatri

Lyrics:
Mottiyan Mottiyan Akhiyaan Ve 
Mai Parriyan De Bhen
Jeyon Gurh Te Makhiyaan Ve 
Mere Piche Aashiq Painn    

Mera Kaala Kaala Suit Jeyon, Kaale Badal Ay

Tere Piche Ikk Do Kudiyan, 
Mere Piche Saari Duniya 
Pagal Ay, Pagal Ay 
Tere Piche Ikk Do Kudiyan 
Mere Piche Saari Duniya 
Pagal Ay, Pagal Ay

Chitti Chitti Jhanjhar De Naal, Uchi Addi Paayi Ve
Nakhro Uttey Aayi Jawaani, Milk Te Jivve Malaayi Ve. 
Charhai Ve Mere Koke Di 
Larhai Mundeya Ch Mere Roke Di 
Aashiq Mere Galli Galli, Mai Copy Chann De Totte Di 

Inna Saareya Vich’on Koi Na Mere Kaabil Ay 

Tere Piche Ikk Do Kudiyan 
Mere Piche Saari Dunia 
Pagal Ay, Pagal Ay
Tere Piche Ikk Do Kudiyan 
Mere Piche Saari Dunia
Pagal Ay, Pagal Ay

Yes Sir, 
Meri Number 1 Par Doon 11 Tujhe 10 Mein
Aankhein Teri Shady Tujhe Chaiye Ni Chashme
Ghuma Na Mujhe Peeche Lele Fere Khaa Le Kasmein
Ye Hanskey Jo Humpey Chalari Hai Tu Asley
Tu Daagti Hai Goli
Bolo Chahti Kya Ho Ji 
Itna Bada Hogayi Ho, Humse Shaadi Karogi
Naam Panther Hai Mera Hume Jaanti To Hogi
Ek Baat Puchu Dosto Ki Bhabhi Banogi
Haye Ram,
Kare Bade Kaand
Humse Rap Game Me Sab Bade Pareshan
Homeground Pehle Show Pe The Lage Pade Jaam
Tabhi Naam Lete Izzat Se Bade Bade Naam
Haye Ram,
Kare Bade Kaand
Meri Fantasy Dark Aur Tu Lage Manne Chand
Mai Dikhadu Tujhe Taare Bhare Din Me Meri Jaan
Diya Dil Tujhe Pehle Aur Ab Deta Hu Zubaan!

Shine Maarda Hussan Kudi Da, 
Maare Laat Jawaani Ve
Ohda Naam Kaptaan, Haaye Jihdi 
Mai Marjaani Deewani Ve. 
Gaani Taunh Saraahi Ch,
Nakk Sharp Lakk Golaayi Ch
Tornado Nu Piche Chad Da
Nakhra Mera Tabaahi Ch

Akhiyaan Meriyan Maldive Da Sagar Ay

Tere Piche Ikk Do Kudiyan 
Mere Piche Saari Duniya 
Pagal Ay, Pagal Ay
Tere Piche Ikk Do Kudiyan 
Mere Piche Saari Duniya
Pagal Ay, Pagal Ay
